BT 0 g /F2 15 Tf 194.4 750 Td (WHY MORNINGS ARE HARD WITH ADHD) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 50 740 m 562 740 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 715 Td (If mornings feel like your personal nemesis, you're not lazy.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 698 Td (ADHD brains have specific challenges that make mornings harder:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 681 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 664 Td (1. SLEEP INERTIA: ADHD brains take longer to 'boot up') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 647 Td (   Your prefrontal cortex \(planning/decision brain\) is sluggish) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 630 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 613 Td (2. TIME BLINDNESS: You genuinely don't feel time passing) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 596 Td (   '5 more minutes' turns into 45 without you noticing) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 579 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 562 Td (3. DECISION FATIGUE: Every choice costs more mental energy) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 545 Td (   What to wear, what to eat, what to bring = overwhelming) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 528 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 511 Td (4. TRANSITION DIFFICULTY: Switching from sleep to action is HARD) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 494 Td (   Your brain resists changing states \(this is neurological, not moral\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 477 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 460 Td (5. WORKING MEMORY ISSUES: You forget steps mid-routine) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 443 Td (   Start brushing teeth, get distracted, forget breakfast) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 426 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 409 Td (6. DOPAMINE DEFICIT: Routine tasks produce zero dopamine) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 392 Td (   Your brain screams 'BORING' and seeks stimulation instead) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 375 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 358 Td (THE GOOD NEWS:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 341 Td (You don't need more willpower. You need better SYSTEMS.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 324 Td (This planner gives you external structure so your brain doesn't) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 307 Td (have to work so hard. Let the system do the thinking.) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
