BT 0 g /F2 15 Tf 237.60000000000002 750 Td (THE 3-ANCHOR SYSTEM) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 50 740 m 562 740 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 715 Td (Instead of a complex morning routine, build around 3 ANCHORS.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 699 Td (Anchors are non-negotiable actions that everything else attaches to.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 683 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 667 Td (ANCHOR 1: THE WAKE-UP ANCHOR) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 651 Td (This is what pulls you out of bed. Choose ONE:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 635 Td (  [ ] Alarm across the room \(must physically get up\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 619 Td (  [ ] Light therapy lamp on timer) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 603 Td (  [ ] Phone alarm in bathroom) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 587 Td (  [ ] Coffee maker on auto-timer \(smell gets you up\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 571 Td (  [ ] Accountability partner texts/calls) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 555 Td (  My wake-up anchor: _________________________________) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 539 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 523 Td (ANCHOR 2: THE BODY ANCHOR) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 507 Td (This 'turns on' your body and brain. Choose ONE:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 491 Td (  [ ] Splash cold water on face immediately) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 475 Td (  [ ] 2-minute stretch routine \(same every day\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 459 Td (  [ ] Step outside for 60 seconds of sunlight) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 443 Td (  [ ] Quick shower \(no decisions - same temp, same products\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 427 Td (  [ ] 10 jumping jacks right out of bed) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 411 Td (  My body anchor: ____________________________________) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 395 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 379 Td (ANCHOR 3: THE LAUNCH ANCHOR) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 363 Td (This is your 'out the door' signal. Choose ONE:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 347 Td (  [ ] Grab launch pad bag \(pre-packed night before\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 331 Td (  [ ] Set 'leaving NOW' alarm 5 min before deadline) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 315 Td (  [ ] Keys + phone + wallet checkpoint at door) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 299 Td (  [ ] Partner/roommate 5-minute warning) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 283 Td (  My launch anchor: __________________________________) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 267 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 251 Td (RULE: Do your 3 anchors in ORDER, every single day.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 235 Td (Everything else can flex. The anchors don't.) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
